SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Outgoing Healing by 10%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: At the start of the battle, immediately regenerates 1 Skill Point.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases ATK by 12%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases DEF by 15%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Ice DMG by 10%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: After the wearer uses their Ultimate, their CRIT DMG increases by 25% for 2 turn(s).

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Physical DMG by 10%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Reduces DMG taken by 8%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Quantum DMG by 10%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Lightning DMG by 10%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: When the wearer uses their Skill, increases the wearer's ATK by 20% for 1 turn(s).

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Wind DMG by 10%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: After the wearer uses their Ultimate, their action is Advanced Forward by 25%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases SPD by 6%.

SetEffects.Pieces4: When the wearer uses a Follow-up ATK, increases the wearer's ATK by 6% for every time the Follow-up ATK deals DMG. This effect can stack up to 8 time(s) and lasts for 3 turn(s). This effect is removed the next time the wearer uses a Follow-up ATK.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases ATK by 12%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: For every DoT the enemy target is afflicted with, the wearer will ignore 6% of its DEF when dealing DMG to it. This effect is valid for a max of 3 DoTs.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases DMG dealt to enemies with debuffs by 12%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Break Effect by 16%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: When the wearer uses their Ultimate on an ally, all allies' Break Effect increases by 30% for 2 turn(s). This effect cannot be stacked.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Break Effect by 16%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: If the wearer's Break Effect is 150% or higher, the Break DMG dealt to the enemy target ignores 10% of their DEF. If the wearer's Break Effect is 250% or higher, the Super Break DMG dealt to the enemy target additionally ignores 15% of their DEF.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases ATK by 12%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by 6%. After the wearer uses a Follow-up ATK, increases DMG dealt by Ultimate by 36%, lasting for 1 turn(s).

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases SPD by 6%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: When using Skill or Ultimate on one ally target, increases the ability target's CRIT DMG by 18%, lasting for 2 turn(s). This effect can stack up to 2 time(s).

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases CRIT Rate by 8%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases ATK by 12%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases Quantum DMG by 10%.

125.Name: Warrior Goddess of Sun and Thunder

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases SPD by 6%.
SetEffects.Pieces4: When the wearer or their memosprite provides healing to ally targets other than themselves, the wearer gains "Gentle Rain," which lasts for 2 turn(s) and can only trigger once per turn. While the wearer has "Gentle Rain," SPD increases by 6% and all allies' CRIT DMG increases by 15%. This effect cannot stack.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases CRIT DMG by 16%.

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases the wearer's ATK by 12%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's ATK increases by an extra 12%.

Increases the wearer's DEF by 15%. When the wearer's Effect Hit Rate is 50% or higher, the wearer gains an extra 15% DEF.
Increases the wearer's CRIT DMG by 16%. When the wearer's current CRIT DMG reaches 120% or higher, after entering battle, the wearer's CRIT Rate increases by 60% until the end of their first attack.
Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by 8%. When the wearer's current CRIT Rate reaches 50% or higher, the DMG dealt by the wearer's Ultimate and Follow-up ATK increases by 15%.
Increases the wearer's Break Effect by 16%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 145 or higher, the wearer's Break Effect increases by an extra 20%.
Increases the wearer's Energy Regeneration Rate by 5%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's action is Advanced Forward by 40% immediately upon entering battle.

Increases the wearer's Effect RES by 10%. When the wearer's Effect RES is at 30% or higher, all allies' CRIT DMG increases by 10%.
Increases the wearer's ATK by 12%. When the wearer's SPD is equal to or higher than 135/160, the wearer deals 12%/18% more DMG.
Increases wearer's Energy Regeneration Rate by 5%. Increases DMG by 10% for all other allies that are of the same Type as the wearer.
Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by 4%. When an enemy target gets defeated, the wearer's CRIT DMG increases by 4%, stacking up to 10 time(s).

314.Name: Izumo Gensei and Takama Divine Realm

SetEffects.Pieces2: Increases the wearer's ATK by 12%. When entering battle, if at least one teammate follows the same Path as the wearer, then the wearer's CRIT Rate increases by 12%.

When an ally uses a Follow-up ATK, the wearer gains 1 stack of Merit, stacking up to 5 time(s). Each stack of Merit increases the DMG dealt by the wearer's Follow-up ATKs by 5%. When there are 5 stacks, additionally increases the wearer's CRIT DMG by 25%.
Increases the wearer's SPD by 6%. When the wearer hits an enemy target that has Fire Weakness, the wearer's Break Effect increases by 40%, lasting for 1 turn(s).
Increases the wearer's Energy Regeneration Rate by 5%. If the wearer is not the first character in the team lineup, then increases the ATK of the first character in the team lineup by 12%.
Increases the wearer's CRIT DMG by 16%. When a target summoned by the wearer is on the field, CRIT DMG additionally increases by 32%.
Increases the wearer's Max HP by 12%. When the wearer's Max HP is 5000 or higher, increases the wearer's and their memosprite's CRIT DMG by 28%.
Increases the wearer's SPD by 6%. When the wearer's SPD is 135/180 or higher, the wearer and their memosprite's Outgoing Healing increases by 12%/20%.

When the number of ally targets on the field is not equal to 4, for every 1 additional/missing ally target, increases the DMG dealt by the wearer and their memosprite by 9%/12%, stacking up to 4/3 time(s).
Increases the wearer's ATK by 12%. When the wearer's ATK is higher than or equal to 2400/3600, increases the DoT DMG dealt by 12%/24% respectively.
